<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>기업회원 가입 안내</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h4>{{ user.name }} (기업명: {{ user.company_name }}, 직책: {{ user.position }})님이 가입하셨습니다.</h4>
    <p>가입 시 채용을 희망한 직군은 아래와 같습니다.</p>
    <ul>
    {% for job_group in user._hire_job_groups.all() %}
        <li>{{ job_group.category.title }} | {{ job_group.title }}</li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <div>
        <a href="https://{{ site.domain }}{{ url('admin:members_companyuser_changelist') }}?is_active__exact=0">기업회원 활성화 처리하기</a>
    </div>
    <div>
        <a href="https://{{ site.domain }}{{ url('admin:members_companyuserhirejobgroupwithapprovalstatus_changelist') }}">채용 희망 직군 이력서 열람 승인 요청 처리하기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
